{"tid":2195873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[撐黃圈] Bauhaus 包浩斯應該係難得既黃色企業","createTime":"2020-09-09T12:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T13:41:13.000Z","uid":13745,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"49de5f24163cd5322a12104ae5ced43d46877c95","tid":2195873,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:28:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20140524/LF3RWAVQECE5TCFEG27DVKEIYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20140524%2FLF3RWAVQECE5TCFEG27DVKEIYI%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=dc1acd9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20140524%2FLF3RWAVQECE5TCFEG27DVKEIYI%2F&h=b8a54a66\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20140524/LF3RWAVQECE5TCFEG27DVKEIYI/</a><br />\n黃銳林一直認為，「（六四事件的）價值判斷已經出咗嚟」，荒謬是近年的是非價值全被扭曲。他指當年全港左中右都指共產黨做得不對，近年卻有越來越多聲音力撐「好彩有鎮壓，如果唔係換唔到中國廿年經濟繁榮」，「我每次聽到都好反感。點解唔係話當年如果跟學生搞改革，今日中國會更加繁榮同廉潔呢？究竟（講者）真係純粹無知，抑或出於經濟利益或仕途上嘅計算呢？」"},{"pid":"cffcef8f22aaf21996ef3758ab5d70d7869a64e3","tid":2195873,"uid":13745,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200909/FP7PUHTLD5CLBFM6YYMD6BWGHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200909%2FFP7PUHTLD5CLBFM6YYMD6BWGHQ%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=d636320d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200909%2FFP7PUHTLD5CLBFM6YYMD6BWGHQ%2F&h=63780e10\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200909/FP7PUHTLD5CLBFM6YYMD6BWGHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n早兩日，Bauhaus仲被爆剋扣僱員人工、假期（所以員工玩嘢亂搞display？）。<br />\n不過撇除今年表現，其實Bauhaus近呢幾年都做得唔好，至19年3月全年，盈轉虧，蝕6210萬元；到今年3月止全年，更狂蝕1.72億元。終於，去到今年5月，創辦人兼主席黃銳林，辭公司行政總裁職務。<br />\n<br />\n要知道，要一個老闆級、不涉政治圈嘅人去講政治相關話題，係好難；你仲要一個當時仲有大陸生意嘅上市公司主席，走去講六四？難上加難。不過佢又肯講，而且仲講得好白。<br />\n<br />\n以至今年，Bauhaus更撤出中國市場，主力經營港、澳、台業務。不過，今年3至6月，港、澳同店銷售跌咗41%；台灣都跌38%。"},{"pid":"bf7516f81fa3db0f258dc967d3c1b163a7f27ea2","tid":2195873,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:36:41.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa581ab137b167aca7154ce8e23fedd5c22bd6b","tid":2195873,"uid":8014,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"一撤出大陸市場 即刻扮黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3a5c1c981df6a28479983791752b6a645ad7a8","tid":2195873,"uid":13745,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fa581ab137b167aca7154ce8e23fedd5c22bd6b","tid":2195873,"uid":8014,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"一撤出大陸市場 即刻扮黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:40:03.000Z","msg":"睇哂個post先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4d4d5343441e83e5db4032af7c2d274ff39945","tid":2195873,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2fa581ab137b167aca7154ce8e23fedd5c22bd6b","tid":2195873,"uid":8014,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"一撤出大陸市場 即刻扮黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"2014年講扭曲六四有助支囯發展係荒謬 2020年Bauhaus先撒出支国市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24367e7fde3144f6119781129804d4de7cef6ca","tid":2195873,"uid":53498,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2a4d4d5343441e83e5db4032af7c2d274ff39945","tid":2195873,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2fa581ab137b167aca7154ce8e23fedd5c22bd6b","tid":2195873,"uid":8014,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"一撤出大陸市場 即刻扮黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/no